                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are couple of problems in obdfilter-survey:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Type of test brw i.e. &quot;g&quot; was not followed with npages,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Target netdisk was not set properly and&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Echo client should not use async IO.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I will attach a patch to address these problems.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
